column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Wednesday March 10 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: Traffic Alert for E Vine St:
column4: The roadway is scheduled to be down to one lane between S Limestone and Hernando Aly from 11:00 a.m. to 3 p.m. (approximate) for emergency electric utility repairs.

column3: Traffic Alert for E Vine St:
column4: Motorists are encouraged to seek an alternate route if possible.
